snippet.description:
#Adipurush #RamSiyaRam 

ADIPURUSH 
CELEBRATING VICTORY OF GOOD OVER EVIL

Gulshan Kumar and T-Series present
A T-Series Films and Retrophiles production 
Starring Prabhas, Saif Ali Khan, Kriti Sanon, Sunny Singh,
Directed by Om Raut.
Produced by Bhushan Kumar, Krishan Kumar, Om Raut, Prasad Sutar, Rajesh Nair

#Adipurush releases IN THEATRES on 16 June 2023 in 3D! 

Watch it in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam.

snippet.title: MVP OR WHAT | JONATHAN IS LIVE | BGMI!
snippet.description:
If you liked the Video don’t forget to Like, Share and Subscribe.

Hey Guys, 
Welcome to my Youtube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."
I Stream BGMI regularly, I also enjoy playing Valorant and other fun games once in a while!
I upload videos regarding Tutorials for BGMI, Funny Highlights, Intense Fights, Crate Openings, Vlogs, etc.

snippet.title: Gasoline Workers बनकर घुसे Abhijeet और Purvi एक घर में | CID | Viral Videos | 31st May 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

A man who was followed by a bunch of goons meets with an accident. The lady from the car comes out to save him. He says something strange to which shocks her as well. What did the guy tell her? And is it somewhere related to the case? To know more, keep watching the episode.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra 
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all the episodes of CID thematic series:  
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIW-pWTn1xxqLezRSU39P_D4

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 50 Teaser - 31st May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

--------------

Join us for an insightful conversation with Nitin Gadkari, an esteemed Indian politician and the current Minister of Road Transport and Highways of India, on our latest podcast episode! 🌟

In this engaging discussion, we delve into Mr. Gadkari's visionary approach to infrastructure development, sustainable transportation, and his unwavering commitment to transforming India's road network. As one of the key architects behind numerous ambitious projects, he shares valuable insights on building world-class highways, promoting electric mobility, and implementing innovative solutions to tackle the challenges of urban congestion and pollution.

Get ready to gain a deeper understanding of the transformative initiatives spearheaded by Mr. Gadkari, as he discusses the significance of renewable energy in transportation, the integration of smart technologies, and the promotion of alternative fuels. Discover how his innovative thinking and strategic planning are paving the way for a greener, more efficient, and digitally connected India.

Beyond infrastructure, we explore Mr. Gadkari's broader vision for economic growth, job creation, and the development of rural areas. Join us for this inspiring conversation with Nitin Gadkari, a dynamic leader who is shaping the future of India's transportation landscape. Tune in to gain valuable insights and be part of the journey towards a sustainable and prosperous nation. Don't miss out - subscribe to our channel and hit the notification bell to stay updated with our latest episodes!

snippet.title: IAS Suraj Tiwari with Vikas Sir। UPSC Topper 2022। Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Suraj Tiwari has secured 917th rank in the Civil Services Examination 2022. In this video he is sharing his journey of preparation. This video will definitely motivate you.

Team Drishti wishes Suraj a very successful and fruitful career.

सूरज तिवारी ने 2022 की सिविल सेवा परीक्षा में 917वीं रैंक हासिल की है। इस वीडियो में     सूरज तैयारी के अनुभव साझा कर रहे हैं। इस वीडियो से निश्चित ही आपकी तैयारी और बेहतर हो सकेगी। 

टीम दृष्टि की ओर से सूरज को सफल और सार्थक करियर की असीम शुभकामनाएँ।

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵
𝐒𝐮𝐛𝐬𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐞 𝐃𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐢 𝐈𝐀𝐒 𝐒𝐡𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐧𝐞𝐥 :

डिजिटल संसार में अधिक रचनात्मक भागीदारी के उद्देश्य से हमने Drishti IAS Shorts के रूप में एक और यूट्यूब चैनल लॉन्च किया है। शॉर्ट्स के लिये निर्धारित समय-सीमा में, इसमें हम रोचक कंटेंट प्रस्तुत करेंगे।

इस लिंक पर जाकर सब्सक्राइब करें: https://drishti.link/Drishti-IAS-Shorts

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

𝐆𝐒 𝐅𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞 (𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐬 + 𝐌𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬) 𝐎𝐧𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐞/𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞:

👉 For 𝐟𝐞𝐞, 𝐀𝐝𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧 and 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 of this course visit this link: https://drishti.link/Online-Course or download the 𝐃𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐢 𝐋𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐀𝐩𝐩.

👉 To know the 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐨 𝐫𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 through our website click on this link: https://drishti.link/foundation-course

👉 𝐓𝐨 𝐠𝐞𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 about this 𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐬𝐀𝐩𝐩 𝐨𝐫 𝐒𝐌𝐒 "𝐆𝐒" on this number: 𝟗𝟑𝟏𝟏𝟒𝟎𝟔𝟒𝟒𝟐

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐬 (𝐇𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐢 𝐋𝐢𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐬):

👉 For 𝐟𝐞𝐞, 𝐀𝐝𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧 and 𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐝𝐞𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐬 of 𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐫𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞 (Hindi Literature and other courses): http://bit.ly/2vGNj72

👉 𝐃𝐞𝐦𝐨 𝐜𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐬 playlist- http://bit.ly/2qyY1cW

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

👉 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐬 𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐒𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐬 की पुस्तकें (संपूर्ण सेट एक साथ) खरीदने के लिये निम्नलिखित लिंक्स का प्रयोग करें:

𝐃𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐢 𝐖𝐞𝐛𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐞: https://bit.ly/30LLMbt

localized.title: IAS Suraj Tiwari with Vikas Sir। UPSC Topper 2022। Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Suraj Tiwari has secured 917th rank in the Civil Services Examination 2022. In this video he is sharing his journey of preparation. This video will definitely motivate you.

Team Drishti wishes Suraj a very successful and fruitful career.

सूरज तिवारी ने 2022 की सिविल सेवा परीक्षा में 917वीं रैंक हासिल की है। इस वीडियो में     सूरज तैयारी के अनुभव साझा कर रहे हैं। इस वीडियो से निश्चित ही आपकी तैयारी और बेहतर हो सकेगी। 

टीम दृष्टि की ओर से सूरज को सफल और सार्थक करियर की असीम शुभकामनाएँ।

snippet.description:

Episode 3785: Sapna Ka Jawab
--------------------------------------------------------
Sapna's father quizzes Pyaarelal with questions. Pyaarelal is also questioned about his previous relationships, which makes everyone uncomfortable. Babita and Madhavi talk about Sapna's father's many queries in the kitchen. Finally, Pyaarelal and Sapna have a private conversation, and Sapna apologizes for her father's behavior. Later, Pyaarelal receives an unusual call regarding purchasing a saree for his wife. What will Sapna think of this? Stay tuned for additional information!

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: निर्जला एकादशी व्रत कथा || Nirjala Ekadashi Vrat Katha || एकादशी की कथा
snippet.description:
निर्जला एकादशी व्रत कथा || Nirjala Ekadashi Vrat Katha || एकादशी की कथा
Today on 30 May 2023, We are presenting the video of Nirjala Ekadashi Ki Katha. 
Nirjala Ekadashi is one of the most popular ekadashi among all the ekadashis. Nirjala Ekadashi is celebrated on the eleventh day of Shukla paksh in Jyestha month. In this Nirjala Ekadashi vrat katha video we have show the complete nirjala ekadashi vrat katha mentioned in puran and also the lok katha of Nirjala ekadashi. Nirjala ekadashi is also known as Bhim Ekadashi, Bhimsen ekadashi, Pandav nirjala ekadashi or bhim gyaras in y.  you may be wondering nirjala ekadashi kab hai ? nirjala ekadashi 2023 is on May 30 2023. Let us watch Nirjala Ekadashi ki katha and pray to lord visnhu to bless us all.
ज्येष्ठ मास में शुक्ल पक्ष में जो एकादशी हो, उसका  पूरी निष्ठा से निर्जल व्रत करो। केवल कुल्ला या आचमन करने के लिये मुख में जल डाल सकते हो, उसको छोड़कर और किसी प्रकार का जल विद्वान् मनुष्य मुख में न डाले, अन्यथा व्रत भंग हो जाता है। एकादशी को सूर्योदय से लेकर दूसरे दिन के सूर्योदय तक मनुष्य जल का त्याग करे तो यह व्रत पूर्ण होता है। अगले दिन द्वादशी को निर्मल प्रभातकाल में स्नान करके ब्राह्मणों तथा जरूरतमंदों को यथाशक्ति दान करे। इस प्रकार सब कार्य पूरा करके भोजन करे। वर्षभर में जितनी एकादशियाँ होती हैं, उन सबका फल निर्जला एकादशी के सेवन से मनुष्य प्राप्त कर लेता है; इसमें  कोई सन्देह नहीं है। शंख, चक्र और गदा धारण करने वाले भगवान् केशव ने मुझसे कहा था कि ‘यदि मानव सब कुछ छोड़कर मेरी शरण में आ जाय और एकादशी को निराहार रहे तो वह सब पापों से छूट जाता है।’
एकादशी व्रत करने वाले मनुष्य के पास विशालकाय, विकराल आकृति और काले रंग वाले दण्ड-पाशधारी भयंकर यमदूत नहीं जाते। अन्तकाल में पीताम्बरधारी, सौम्य स्वभाव वाले, हाथ में सुदर्शन धारण करने वाले और मन के समान वेगशाली विष्णु दूत आकर इस वैष्णव पुरुष को भगवान् विष्णु के धाम में ले जाते हैं। अतः निर्जला एकादशी को पूर्ण यत्न करके उपवास करना चाहिये। तुम भी सब पापों की शान्ति के लिये यत्न के साथ उपवास और श्रीहरि का पूजन करो। स्त्री हो या पुरुष, यदि उसने मेरु पर्वत के बराबर भी महान् पाप किया हो तो वह सब एकादशी के प्रभाव से भस्म हो जाता है। जो मनुष्य उस दिन जल के नियम का पालन करता है, वह पुण्य का भागी होता है, उसे एक-एक पहर में कोटि-कोटि स्वर्ण मुद्रा दान करने का फल प्राप्त होता सुना गया है। मनुष्य निर्जला एकादशी के दिन स्नान, दान, जप, होम आदि जो कुछ भी करता है, वह सब अक्षय होता है, यह भगवान् श्रीकृष्ण का कथन है।

#निर्जला एकादशी #NirjalaEkadashi #EkadashiVratKatha #एकादशी  #PandavEkadashiKatha

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3784 | 30 May 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3784: Ek Ghante Ki Meeting
--------------------------------------------------------
To meet Sapna and Kalpana, everyone gets ready, and Popatlal offers his greetings to God for sending 'rishtas' for him. Popatlal prays that Kalpana and Sapna should not get to know about his other name. He welcomes Chamapaklal and Mahila Mandal at his house for help.  Pyaarelal is delighted to meet Sapna. Could Pyaarelal's life be altered by this encounter? Will Pyarelal get married this time? Watch the episode to know more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3784, 30 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: What I Bought From South Africa - Africa Shopping Haul - Making Cafe Style Irani Chai at Home
snippet.description:
Product Website. https://masaladrops.com/

Use promo code “YUMMY15” so you can get 15% discount and free shipping on all products.

Zaffron foods holder of brand “masala drops” offering an innovative range of 100% Natural - liquid spices in soluble form which is convenient to use and enhances the flavour & aroma of the food. They manufacture the products in a patented nanotechnology process and the facility is incubated with MABIF - (National Bank for Agriculture and Rural Development- NABARD), which adheres to the strictest quality standards, from sourcing to packaging. It is certified for GMP, ISO 22000, HACCP standards and an USFDA-registered.

MFG PROCESS:
Sourcing Spices Whole Raw material. Spices Oils (Oil extraction from Spices) Steam distillation of Spice oils to convert drops form. MFG unit is in Madurai and products are 100% natural and supported by Nabard - Mabif Agri - Madurai. This is not essence, synthetic/ Artificial flavor. Products are pure spices with all goodness in liquid form.
---------------------------------

snippet.description:
Aaj Masala Kitchen Me Ban Raha Hai 𝐇𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞 𝐊𝐢 𝟔 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐥𝐢 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐞. Healthy Aur Tasty Gluten-Free Recipe Banaiye Ek Khas Trick Se. 

#Vegthalirecipe #Ragirotirecipe #WeightlossRecipe #7DaysThali #MasalaKitchenThaliRecipe #MultigrainChapati #JowarKiRoti #ChawalRotiRecipe #RagiParatha #LessOilHealthyRecipe #trending 
----------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐔𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐚𝐝: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVtKBj3j-Xc

Please Follow Me On:
👍𝐅𝐚𝐜𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐨𝐤: https://www.facebook.com/masalakitchenrecipe
📸𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦: https://www.instagram.com/masalakitchenbypoonam/

Subscribe Karein Humare 2nd YouTube Channel ko:
▶️𝐌𝐚𝐚 𝐘𝐞𝐡 𝐊𝐚𝐢𝐬𝐞 𝐊𝐚𝐫𝐮𝐧?: https://www.youtube.com/c/Maayehkaisekarun

🌐𝐖𝐞𝐛𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤 - https://www.poonamdevnani.com/
----------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐓𝐄𝐃 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒:
Office 6 Tiffin Recipe
https://youtu.be/8FLvAP2tX4U

Tiffin Recipe For Whole Week
https://youtu.be/3lnvzhIgpfc

6 School Lunch Idea
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-N2hTLODFjE

Raagi ke Papad
https://youtu.be/6XdfLXQYvho

Easy Sooji Papad Recipe
https://youtu.be/fTwpXZ2TA5c

Instant Dahi Vada Recipe
https://youtu.be/0LwnKmCjTg8
-------------------------------------
✍🏻𝗜𝗡𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗗𝗜𝗘𝗡𝗧𝗦:
 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏:
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup
* Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta (ज्वार का आटा) - 1Cup
* Ghee (घी) - Some  
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐:
* Water (पानी) - 2 Cup
* Oil (तेल) - Some
* Salt (नमक) - Some
* Ragi Flour/Nachni (रागी का आटा) - 1 Cup
* Boiled Potato (उबले आलू)
* Green Chilli (हरी मिर्च)
* Corainder Leaves (धनिया पत्ती)
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑:
Normal Wheat Flour Chapati
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒:
* Rice flour (चावल का आटा) - 1 Cup
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟓:
* Rice
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟔:
* Multigrain Flour (मल्टीग्रेन आटा) -  1 Cup
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup

✍🏻𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐉𝐨𝐰𝐚𝐫 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta to it. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Dal, Bhindi, Curd & Sproud Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐚𝐠𝐢 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐚, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Then knead the dough adding little water gradually to make firm and smooth dough. Then take a dough ball & fill the filling in it. Then flatten them with the fingers. Roast the Paratha & serve the Healthy Ragi Tawa Paratha Recipe along with Mix Dal, Dry Karele, Raita & Green Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Rice Flour. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it. 
Turn the heat to high. Wait for 3 steams and turn off the heat & release the pressure. Serve hot & enjoy with Chhole, Salad, Curd & Dry Arbi ki sabzi. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟓 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐢𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, take a plate & put some Multigrain Flour & bind the dough by adding some water gradually. Cover & keep aside for some time. Then make Chapati & serve with Dal, Sabzi, Salad & Dahi Bhalla. In this way, 7 Days special thali will get ready easily. 
-----------------------------
मल्टीग्रेन रोटी रेसिपी, ग्लूटेन फ्री चपाती रेसिपी, चावल की रोटी रेसिपी, रागी रोटी रेसिपी, ज्वार की रोटी रेसिपी, हेल्दी चावल रोटी, रागी रोटी के फायदे, ज्वार रोटी के स्वास्थ्य लाभ, ग्लूटेन-फ्री आटा कैसे बनाएं, ग्लूटेन-फ्री रागी रोटी, रागी रोटी के लिए टिप्स और ट्रिक्स...!

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐚𝐠𝐢 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐚, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Then knead the dough adding little water gradually to make firm and smooth dough. Then take a dough ball & fill the filling in it. Then flatten them with the fingers. Roast the Paratha & serve the Healthy Ragi Tawa Paratha Recipe along with Mix Dal, Dry Karele, Raita & Green Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Rice Flour. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it. 
Turn the heat to high. Wait for 3 steams and turn off the heat & release the pressure. Serve hot & enjoy with Chhole, Salad, Curd & Dry Arbi ki sabzi. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟓 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐢𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, take a plate & put some Multigrain Flour & bind the dough by adding some water gradually. Cover & keep aside for some time. Then make Chapati & serve with Dal, Sabzi, Salad & Dahi Bhalla. In this way, 7 Days special thali will get ready easily. 
-----------------------------

snippet.title: 'Bharat Mata Ki Jai' slogans reverberate in new Parliament as PM Modi arrives in Lok Sabha
snippet.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi received a thunderous welcome in the new Parliament on May 28. Earlier, today PM Modi unveiled the plaque to mark the inauguration of the new Parliament building. PM Modi installed the sacred ‘Sengol’ in the new Parliament building. Later, he felicitated the workers who helped in the building and development of the new Parliament building.

snippet.title: Debt ceiling explained in Hindi | American Economic Crisis | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the Debt Ceiling crisis of USA and why America will never be like Sri Lanka.

#debtceiling #worldaffairs #abhiandniyu 

In our informative and engaging video, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges," we delve into one of the most critical aspects of economic governance: the debt ceiling. Join us on a journey through the complexities of national debt, government spending, and the mechanisms in place to manage these fiscal challenges.

With a clear and concise narrative, we break down the debt ceiling concept, explaining its purpose and implications. Our expert hosts provide a comprehensive overview of how the debt ceiling functions within the framework of a country's financial system and explore the practical effects it has on government operations and the economy at large.

As the video progresses, we explore the historical context behind the establishment of debt ceilings and how they have evolved over time. We shed light on the reasons governments may hit their debt limit and the consequences that can arise when the ceiling is breached. Our analysis includes the potential effects on financial markets, credit ratings, borrowing costs, and public trust in the government's fiscal responsibility.

Additionally, we examine the intricate relationship between the debt ceiling and the political landscape. Through case studies and real-world examples, we explore how debates and negotiations surrounding debt ceiling increases or suspensions often become contentious and polarizing. We discuss the various strategies employed by governments to address the debt ceiling and the potential implications for the economy and citizens.

Throughout the video, we present clear graphics, charts, and data visualizations to enhance understanding and illustrate the key concepts discussed. We ensure that even viewers without prior knowledge of economics or government finance can follow along and grasp the significance of the debt ceiling in the broader financial ecosystem.

Whether you are a student, a concerned citizen, or a professional seeking to expand your knowledge of economic governance, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges" offers valuable insights and a comprehensive overview of this critical aspect of fiscal policy. Join us on this informative journey and gain a deeper understanding of the debt ceiling's impact on national economies and everyday lives.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

snippet.title: China ने सरेआम तोड़ी मस्जिद, मुस्लिमों को पीटा, डरे 56 मुस्लिम देश !Najiaying Mosque News|Uighur |OIC
snippet.description:
China ने सरेआम तोड़ी बड़ी मस्जिद, डर के भागे 56 मुस्लिम देश ! Najiaying Mosque News |Muslims in China|OIC

China's cruelty to minority communities has yet again been glimpsed in the country’s southwest as the government is calling on protesters to turn themselves in after a crowd clashed with police over plans to demolish a mosque. The action from authorities came as President Xi Jinping’s government tightens control over religion and society.

China के दक्षिण-पश्चिम क्षेत्र में स्थित मुस्लिम बाहुल्य इलाके में स्थानीय जनता और पुलिस के बीच भिड़ंत हो गई. इसके पीछे की वजह ये थी कि स्थानीय पुलिस इलाके में मौजूद सदियों पुरानी मस्जिद की गुंबददार छत को गिराने के लिए आई हुई थी. इसी को रोकने के लिए स्थानीय लोगों और पुलिस के बीच भिड़ंत हो गई.

#chianuighurmuslims #muslimsinchina #uighursmuslim

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3783 - 29 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3783: Do Do Rishte
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak ultimately succeeds in getting a leave of absence from work, but his manager is still interested in Pyaarelal's tale. Taarak explains to his boss why Pyaarelal, a.k.a. Popatlal, has been single and how being single has made his life miserable. Taarak's manager understands and gives him permission to go a little early. When Pyaarelal learns that his friend Taarak is returning, he is delighted. Champaklal is one of the elderly people, thus the Gokuldham women and Pyaarelel thought to invite him to the meeting. Pyaarelal receives a call later about another marriage proposal, but the bride's family prefers his original name, Popatlal. Now, what will he do?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3783, 29 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap

Ekam confronts Nehmat and forces the truth out of her. He blames Jasmine for ruining his life and vows to exact his revenge on her. Meanwhile, Renuka overhears Sartaj's conversation with the doctor and promises to keep Nehmat's pregnancy a secret. Will she keep her word?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: Pankaj क्यों कर रहा है बर्तन से अपना Face Hide? | CID | सी.आई.डी | Master Plan | 27 May 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ

Ravi, while returning from a party with his family loses consciousness when he witnesses the bizarre sight of an unusual biker on the highway. When he regains consciousness his family was nowhere to be found. He contacts Abhijeet who reaches the spot. He too is in for a shock. Abhijeet shoots the biker but he goes unhurt which shocks him. The bullet just passes through him. Watch to know what happens next. 

Show Name: CID
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi

The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police.
